instance one : One (AddMonoidAlgebra k G) :=
  ⟨single 0 1⟩
end One
instance nonUnitalSemiring [Semiring k] [AddSemigroup G] : NonUnitalSemiring (AddMonoidAlgebra k G) :=
  { AddMonoidAlgebra.nonUnitalNonAssocSemiring with
    zero := 0
    mul := (· * ·)
    add := (· + ·)
    mul_assoc := sorry }
